race.comment: WHISKEY WHISKERS (2) lines up chasing another win after rocketing around the this track 525m in 29.61 on October 11. Smart win latest and looks a key chance again here. WEBLEC SNOOP (1) scored (30.31) last time out at this track in a Special conditions SF and will break from box 1 for the first time. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. One of the leading chances again. COOLABAH STATION (6) has recorded back to back wins, the quickest two back at Bendigo in 27.87. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. In great form and can continue his winning ways. TREBLE BEERS (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.
